  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a FontForge</title>

    <para>
      The <application>FontForge</application> package contains an outline font
editor that lets you create your own postscript, truetype, opentype,
cid-keyed, multi-master, cff, svg and bitmap (bdf, FON, NFNT) fonts, or edit
existing ones.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

